Mélisse & Guido! Kind sweet souls! Thank you for inviting me to witness your love in Tuscany this weekend. I am honored and oh-so grateful to be a part of your world. Leave it to filmmakers to have the most aesthetically stunning wedding. And thanks for trusting me to shoot the whole thing on my super 8 amongst some of the most badass cinematographers in the game. Sheeeeesh💋❤️ I love you two. Cheers! Let’s continue making art together for eternity🥂

Landshuter Hochzeit is a reenactment of a wedding that took place between a Polish princess and German Prince in 1475. 2,000 participants in Landshut,Bavaria,Germany partake. Some of those participants are my family! What a beautiful festival. I’m good on German food for a while though…

In 2023, I prioritized family and relocated from LA to my hometown, NY. Although there were many tough moments and a couple rock bottoms, I feel stronger and more determined than ever. I fell in love, made some beautiful new connections, and strengthened old ones. I’m grateful for all my friends who have stuck by me. I love you! 2024 is gonna be great❤️ (beautiful pic by @joeperri , makeup by @taylertreadwell )
